graph TD
    %% AgentRx feedback loop from upstream issue #30

    Admin[👤 Admin User]
    UI[🖥️ Admin UI]
    Proposal[💡 Improvement Proposal<br/>Observed quality gap / desired behavior]
    AgentRx[🩺 AgentRx<br/>Analyze system + recommend changes]
    Review{✅ Approve<br/>recommended changes?}
    Refine[🔁 Revise proposal<br/>or keep for backlog]
    Orchestrator[🔐 Admin Change Orchestrator]

    AgentCfg[🤖 Agent Configuration<br/>Top-level instruction updates]
    GenieCfg[🧞 Genie Configuration<br/>Add/remove tables and Genies<br/>Room-level instructions]
    MetadataCfg[🧱 Metadata / Smart ETL<br/>Columns, comments, abbreviations]

    AdminOps[⚙️ Admin-Level Operations]
    Refresh[🚀 Refresh deployed agent context<br/>and data access configuration]
    Runtime[💬 End User Runtime]
    Feedback[📈 Better accuracy, curation, and speed]

    Admin --> UI --> Proposal --> AgentRx --> Review
    Review -->|No| Refine --> Proposal
    Review -->|Yes| Orchestrator

    Orchestrator --> AgentCfg
    AgentCfg --> GenieCfg
    GenieCfg --> MetadataCfg
    MetadataCfg --> AdminOps --> Refresh --> Runtime --> Feedback
    Feedback -. informs .-> Admin

